TITLE: Using React Hook for ElectricSQL Integration
DESCRIPTION: React component example that uses the useShape hook from @electric-sql/react to sync and display data from a Postgres table. The hook fetches data based on specified parameters including table name and WHERE clause.
SOURCE: https://github.com/electric-sql/electric/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-14_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
import { useShape } from "@electric-sql/react"

function Component() {
  const { data } = useShape({
    url: `http://localhost:3000/v1/shape`,
    params: {
      table: `foo`,
      where: `title LIKE 'foo%'`,
    },
  })

  return JSON.stringify(data)
}
```

