TITLE: Firebase Security Rules Structure Example
DESCRIPTION: Example of Firebase security rules structure showing the basic pattern for resource access control.
SOURCE: https://github.com/electric-sql/electric/blob/main/website/blog/posts/2024-11-21-local-first-with-your-existing-api.md#2025-04-14_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
service <<name>> {
  // Match the resource path.
  match <<path>> {
    // Allow the request if the following conditions are true.
    allow <<methods>> : if <<condition>>
  }
}
```

